---wifi

$su
#apt-get update
#apt-get upgrade

#apt-get install firmware-iwlwifi
#modprobe -r iwlwifi
#modprobe iwlwifi
#apt-get install wicd

It may occur after update/upgrade the names for network interfaces to change. Check with ifconfig. This may have
result on your wifi connections.

--- thunar archive manager
$sudo apt-get install thunar-archive-plugin
$sudo apt-get install file-roller

